title: Vassdragskalking app dokumentasjon
text:
This website provides documentation for the liming application.
The current pages are just placeholder (in English). The final website should be translated to Norwegian.

title: Column tests
text: Describe the column tests. Two main types of test:

title: Column tests
text:
1 Instantaneous dissolution
5 columns. Add fixed amount of lime at varying pH.

title: Column tests
text:
2 Overdosing
5 columns. Add different amount of lime at fixed pH.
